Invocation Name: i am
des: I am is a way for Alexa to brighten up your day. Start by saying Alexa I am and she will proceed to tell you how great you are. Alexa will continue to compliment you as long as you want, and she will become your new favorite supporter! She will always be there for you to make sure you feel great.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
